gin: 16px 0;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普总统在前往北卡罗来纳州灾区期间表示，他正在考虑&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I2OgxmHM9vJ5ZjQE0s95g5TNn5OYmDEflK-EBQBveEZutPArAKeDuzhHfh69D6RR-_FgJUn_3m-_vJKIo41IcmZJyAq6nAy4OwSrFTTrAhoUDHki63Qp8CqNrmKIj4HjpV76zOr5Om7ukmIB0XmtVd0srgw-KfKE9PcISiFMVWeWbjM1IsjQ3aLFFXMgtkU4CxGvdRxu5uQvvtdjQxqtkyq43mALY2yYmy6ySLeIdiivogIP3QRO5_GLDucd1RWjvy0Jo4wUKhN-yTqXgTi0s75vspKN9FwfOjLTaHy97KSw4StrFSYNvWsRFhYnCClAsw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;废除联邦紧急&lt;/a&gt;响应机构 FEMA。特朗普批评该机构“让国家失望”，并表示该机构未来可能会减少参与恢复工作。在前往加利福尼亚州调查火灾损失之前，他在北卡罗来纳州阿什维尔露面时提出了批评，该市去年遭受了飓风海伦洪水的破坏。自从 10 月袭击北卡罗来纳州的风暴引发一波声称联邦紧急事务管理署拒绝向共和党社区&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7IyKGCvKjvAz_uDx1380XjaDJhGOuMZ9tdE-bmWhXx8b_iko6jFyUrch7dstVsKwUOJEm5v6U9S_gGsh25P5hUQFaewMuRFbStFPTT-2b16-opaSQzYE_FYoFGBmYMrqM7MMCi9iWZhPS7sh82q5pM-qKTUZwD6KwhzKFJza9EqweAR91kYYgpmepgizVbBnmhyOwXpKQPEyCpmlr6_kuwJ24cSirFI2kzRfGBT3bdnogZRW3DLgdY1qHcLTq9k86e2-_lUab9vTKrtQWQLKKkvQSUOohAci3VIJlNkNvdLehNOD0wCJJX2ULfoXw-r0u2w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;提供援助&lt;/a&gt;的指控（无论是被揭穿还是未经证实）以来，联邦紧急事务管理署一直成为政治焦点。特朗普本人在竞选过程中指责联邦应急管理局&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I8tARcqi4Wizxt9gb-Xv2D41z2H5lCcLqQL_YeLN9Cch15yG6qZLXXYkHSWYDSIBpzqhzHHh5tJEP2j5Hd2yixQ4nkQ_80J3oZYHub2njOR8kNlz15O6imnvrSuITjrpJOSbza2kBFF4DithBzGvozn7kHMaq8kJPTvtD_L5uPUFBmbytiFRmmwQv9Xz07kf2CZNUedX5xhHcjP9K0QsQk_jcdh9uMqCfcSoG2uNrLYtN-1OWzd_-00qNcHOILNTTgphkTZLYhqQksMqwT5VK7ms-ndhjoQSo9oI1_YFmtOvMUktxWhHXHPA6wz-NiRppw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将资金&lt;/a&gt;用于“非法移民”，拜登政府否认了这一言论。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I2OgxmHM9vJ5ZjQE0s95g5TGJZx04yFNwe-HtbfuSpy89GWUjlSTmZEa2yIg7cmCh_ABXNBuultMndp3Gpl0ctNtH0QR9ZOFqCYsFyHEdBFapHsXnJsylSr8g9e9dRuhbWWa9NTAPctrmJdHxyOGJILuw_U9OUl2hF3omiNfXug0yFjMxMwCTbcfxgpDhXjU7i6jsoGDcUR7fBEy1w6_ynKD6l44oVt_SpYSglPoCaI1GdCxMZ7T65G_idU6KhV5h7kbaHTUmCqtit5EDC9chQ3sCp_FYugeIeya-I3xHVVUrNXWT-gTZ-VRJocZVgEBaQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;本周早些时候&lt;/a&gt;，特朗普提出将救灾援助移交给各个州，而不是让联邦政府做出回应，并任命了一名没有明显救灾经验的前海豹突击队队员作为该机构的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7Ixu4jCXe_ijIlDc3rhzV4u7aNqh4VS6j1Hy4G21KoxJlhp00MvmxkZ30DcSGxYA1x3t1_IYg7PYkJTtiBNK4bBf_LJvXmFXmQE32xklZZFcwQC6NE474X2LHtcrtV5s3m48YU0VMDbPBzI-YRq0SVMpvhd7hADprlNN8NYIH3VFtQ7W-stj7CBcg_SGd853_GuCsdKBjcqvMbPluLm0Wb66_ezmfMV5Il4U3MjXR8C8Vk2APkivvCrUdxNvNso8Nz-srGU9T9aRbEGg7dny1pHoTlqETkiBwePS0cVhJHMvmxANpOxV0DzJsJoMJ9LYp72pQjnmHtDvg9QBDhv_pR4vk4k27LsjjmHsNWz8kirWOizeMxt4M40_HbeIdg1RINSNrKUAX0GrQhy_S-vv-QpyzP1G-Mn1e_D-bPDKUkfXOWS8gKE83dlEn0vIs6f7e4-vX-BBFLmcFowGF70LKktk%3D" target="_blank"&gt;临时负责人&lt;/a&gt;。特朗普没有权力解散联邦应急管理局——只有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7Ixu4jCXe_ijIlDc3rhzV4u4ogYd7A3OdisbJwfBgXsWT1kniXY7ZMkTWvpE3B02cr3-OwU7pdeb_FpitH2dvCJ5QsIduT_H8bD0TQOd8FUT0BVk2Az_18kC8zfo7TcF0ygInna79QwG_3blMw438vqQdNQ_nH23AAOCCGBrGsX-7KJIm6GOQZfnOE759aMsfWbnpuoiC2J-GX55A2Mc_m4Fpv8pY6IAt2hEsNdrtAo3xKNycC40UMIOCXvl5AU4xEKrnshfPJTI7UEtcifokndkUKHekb3D5TMeM3quZpLWOx1yaXKayZCVGUatRkWTCXR1p0SPqaKL2ifOEGnccQeRlwQO8n1TyGAr8L_hARuMZg8qu4qoNPcdPIDmjPA7d_DoSiY4b25GFn-yATcyPo-LNKo4eCddm2J6elbBUG00uc5ZotuM5DkP6CJGtCuJkfQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;国会才有这个权力&lt;/a&gt;。但对该机构的反应进行审查之际，该机构&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I