https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcSu_iVSp55uUdwY18gfunb46oZNU84pfyGpMXxi69c_obNWDWA-M11OqrcmMebRPVVeP7bv9Vr6DUdic-LlzdoCOL09lBz9-L6AeAFkX5QDJw-d8nnPw8oge0KTDq0tnSml8_tSrCIDvQVecr9kgwzuE-yKu-5KACdWyKaImzlMHANc5gCjLmmmRKWHhQ5TcI8IU8klNVCUGE1o5GLbEsxlZ_mynuK5ArhPsSNwMfVN10O9BY3PLwxxvKy1A8xqC8DUxhrIo-Tewk1VspiuRmUl2QGZklpAg8YvxQW2DNFenVAohafCV9A_MZtg2BV3GdQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将面临处罚&lt;/a&gt;。尽管特朗普在上任第一天就推迟了对中国征收关税的核心竞选承诺，但他继续&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcTYEOEPpilFt6a9Zshbp6lXDhTNZtGuSAhOsriyZeaEwX0pkNoklKMdtPXOh-MB9HUV8xIYOnGPLU4kaZI8xUXHCfY3u2NUwobdIBpXLj7I9p4KuRS76Fgazhx6oI9tz5gVqLwVoX73UZqx5WWuR1SUSwSkIrDLdEH_tpQ6zbzq9ZcBZkBAMKhitFJufPoROpH0Lgetz1TLgYxbFcqjQvQ2mV0hAUU64BIjVkjxfkayYYOvsBJJlJMFq1o8yT5g7e9mVMtbbFxI0BP5dvo0iq2jKXyDLM_sc3DmqiZjy-_Bof7Qj0bzwBbKhLcWZLEdSWw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;威胁对加拿大和墨西哥征收25%的关税&lt;/a&gt;，这两个美国主要贸易伙伴已承诺迅速报复。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; 78 岁的特朗普出现在一段视频中，视频显示他的两侧是椭圆形办公室总统坚决办公桌上的一张特大印章图像。当他宣布将推动欧佩克削减原油价格时，他成功地&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgceFDE4DAvmQ0qZv8ykGkYBCkq9UuY_pCigrKg1u56bTauH-UD-lBABwmt0mtBSqv172NQtjadyqOwxGSZiGtlqlfZz34jc0Y2DzkKJWsSxPFPekSAXNq6GD7E1BfXBpazHuwoPy-rbWqexYnnRIKjuL_rLGOHbMgxgQbyNcSCq2CQMllajcxMFfucz0SPJ8cmDmzvVnj5QZTBc34ZojYwa522pzwzWOySIDVa2YtvGxWw6xfYX6RjHqcHS79aGAeiFYfLyBrkYUen8U0Ov-2wP6xdDPV7PCKY_WlHJgVPdxGvg56Hiqzf_K9ZSN7eObFIw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;压低了油价&lt;/a&gt;，尽管包括特朗普本人在内的早期总统的类似努力常常被置若罔闻。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcflPG3VOQTZQxO7M8hdLNCiLB04WgT2lKDFnaz9kLKeabxd403TGEmtLgmw9fzwm3QNfInWerwjteoXmtxOJN3c0_ptDHLOadYrY7ZX9q_Ry5psRAbX6vhlMRPGH8N3a-7PZ_pmMGr57ElX-V0Aa6xt_s6_7lCdFEpfpfxVhGc1gnOH8fqc6CQcubH1xSmhebgbTNsGIGAbZwezXkb9_uP9cYwmB0w1lMZnH5L8Rd8rhiDdBXCB3ueindCn1yThQy4wkY_WcGabe6_K1TAzFvyiiLOV8b7m911IJPU_Pvcw2ysVznc0EPt_yHGUM91Px7A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;尽管华尔街支持特朗普&lt;/a&gt;，但也未能逃脱共和党的愤怒。在演讲中，特朗普试图将矛头指向摩根大通和美国银行，在没有证据的情况下指责它们限制接触他所称的“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgccsAQyXlzWLp0KHIg0AezZ15BjVa3HqQMrVSxj9ZPoICZYo4DkcK8B3Dby9JLh_Cpf5ZwHn2mciAzoYPTeZEiG2Oma5BFiH1x090MWI_G0YW1jkWmnKjr5fmQDs01pk4xIZ43v0Y5bglxovSdYhlfJUsGdO1hfvJQpAkSZe7l9uWL5-Jm26i73JsbWWC5t0uw-eSF7yokuRKcsoDnnQY8MG9SdQZ_W-2zXp1aa0o4lqcSmYEp_Ghp3FTKvSG0-Gy4LGNjpOfu0OM-wA0YN0mQX-P1T6kczKUCRtTTjnAjh9UKmPL6uLTl7gnh8PBtYu7NQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;保守派&lt;/a&gt;”客户，而银行认为这是谎言。然而，在美国大规模杀戮不断发生的背景下，银行限制了对一些枪支制造商的贷款。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; 2018 年初佛罗里达州一所高中发生枪击事件后，美国银行此前限制了向生产非军事用途突击型枪支的公司提供&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcQZgZxg_Eji9xZwUNEM3_FLV0JYzxKUBnUy4QiBs9FB6OZsjvIe7saejaGiM8tbkuFVcPJLYbpF6NxWvVEFIV-uaF0F7rouC9Q0ff3qwmmyXMiSzSbEN9LCz7SHoBsBUqi1BKhD5o1DjSWqz82CyXoxXqnAijU51ETGHDOnC97DHQdOb7dYWfJFmvdzmAf10HxHWOHJfPzey_k0HsfpnDAQRCt6TKOI6E7z02r723E0lyk0P0k9MhLJmUshS24EyZMxXX7hvLFt_CLBQPlvfG9orTFGTeZbUR6-BxYzhFL5HfsMeYKPg6WjLoDFfq_aRhw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;贷款&lt;/a&gt;。花旗集团当年也宣布了针对销售枪支的客户的一系列&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcWBHQO9T3WZSMODZ4crcPt0Ap3TFFjRFivcrzdB0IegmedyJ42X7PodxEMetHka_c0vZF6Gq1R0iWbWg0wLL5MhDAqzUnwpjVmMBlwG6R35GGghnR-Ar2quZfWUrz_7xjE3Nvsm5p4x3FI1GxMka6T9wu29HFtnvgNm-7bW3vSPtwKXz-dz2jZar7d6ZSvcqpwCIHcqFWjzF9hhgrmXXrIS-72dFIN6nZAbYXsQmIU6WJ3I7a56ACscNhB2tuql0VSEHMU9VU9qTWybzgIC7M9e6WGhPsEu3-FiwCT2d1g1FkaTEc5GU9THpAnaesIvzO0DUuD8PA9dxB9RIUklDwiGPfIo2QYm-PPq6euUOq2RM3GiFYFD8N6U1ojAKq-twwu7lNZWWBQMMYooVp-KsTfxnhboYCiUm5CJsgROCQH95YPCk7QrIB_LSS85pm8ngiQwJF7Hc_PVIA9iQV_VhvKV1uZruwrRRbnVsUxwB-dMHplu4SqwcMISUuMxYU1bwcQ%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="政策声明链接"&gt;限制&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;em&gt;——玛格丽特·萨瑟林和乔丹·厄布&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;一名联邦法官阻止了&lt;/strong&gt;特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaRkwcfH-0z7-6hIqjOGGt8ys7iIQqn4lKJWxZryG_IsnarygOJJhSDliK3Hxv2ihn9EmvoP1Vx7N5B-A2Zi6YYoYENnqbcP4kB6vFsYdGVI3DCc9OGRSoXxF3rnaASOzmkj2y6k99cLJBiYL_Cd-RKgoHbXCoqgR45YrNiLVhqlofKfs1KLjPFgEkeDdotk6mVeQJKuk4820AFOdsxN08Cu5BWP2Byhp7RlBXds_hlfiJea0ZHZnO_fxJSFphELZ8_vWiZPzhd70Gw-a3smrBUh8nc5W51FmagPdiVYg-i687Wi1f6X2jaF6EsQDwOq7w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;终止与生俱来的公民身份&lt;/a&gt;的行政命令，这是根据美国宪法的简单语言和一个世纪的先例作出的普遍预期的裁决。美国地区法官 John Coughenour 的决定在全国范围内生效，将在 14 天内阻止政府采取任何措施执行特朗普的行政命令，届时随着诉讼的进行，可能会进行更长期的延迟。就在特朗普首次失败的几天前， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcYhJrWjFzX6-5J4TofsQO5ubkJ8o3TEzVO7uJFMIZTSf-OUYAoXUHYtY_SZFnovFxwVWI66NZXYU66C74xy34newVLzoPoHi3kIEW7Q5Rd6p0iurg2lihLyCnMo3Bcb2yy6jFGrLHPEsZDCjiEKQ1jGebqCPpUVlOlwbTbtNsjrMTcmO1SoiiRk0KSb1krO-Dg240NWKNh8acC2UCUXIFPn-awS7AfkFi-h5linb6IxymlSeTuZDccnkxQlkMeQMFWMWgrbGJdmnpTpyrIn6Ver9wN1730jpUD9DqIz9_rw49UrZhq7kFL9BluLplAAGbA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;民主党领导的各州就该措施起诉了&lt;/a&gt;他。据&lt;em&gt;美联社&lt;/em&gt;报道，库格努尔对特朗普的律师说：“这是一项公然违宪的命令。”&lt;em&gt;据美联社&lt;/em&gt;报道，这位由罗纳德·里根任命的法官表示，他不记得曾经见过这样的案件，所质疑的行动如此&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=b121298e7e7e46078e5de16bae6bd34c&amp;amp;_e=Ki8kfM8nx9PN2GAzQVqgcaBYfTlIRQyttiC1WxfiO9iPcwymi0xU8coPCO84gc6NEWvML7AJeJkDq85NDn38SecZQ3KW5SKoiHQnsKsCKtvwSvXgRYu4sr3l8anZyRiSU_WITxkgFCjo21ohLQlyy6T8mYGX_EJekcwyWHxMXOZB5Z9kb0wyihcfOd7evNLjDMDZZkTNekxeG0cM4Yz-ZrQ67hYWFTfBmKjQ4EpXmcKRwK2Q60sdjKpkfPeMDSnulVTtrz4XyYTwlMo6yzvKmEF3OSzNxljMYKERf8OLgK6xlKZ5va6PXEghE9jaDMyjpIJyc79Q2cs0wU6D2y29acKHbMSOwMPQ_cZEeaKSwfHC3Jr9ULh7ZZMC9Acvxno2ZOMRLQ8avo8EoSj8xqfeDRtSyy2c_rX1ZcWD0-vLFwY4K-x7hqSLBoQWwOyRaMKdO7N2Pgc1xiuKQ7RLUxbh9tibJhGaZkvL6aNM-LfI9HyKaKAO8euyur_uagp3j1vJsdd0r6sThXDnQ6PCmk_FMWUgLKUmA98EFW6kf9LPYxjsiEA1Noh8HXszgOgpMevoHtY0wigiwrX1VHCPjNRb9gEFIiqQQ8TCaQwc80C5QBccTlkrmIxPajlfyT9YimImiSq100RLs5PdFB03HYg8rWRUsRENNHtlDoSKxXJq5nnSdT37WKXn4pZ5T3jzRtUX5CRXvtKRrWn2viMRnQqFCwNRESvAnuj09DI75aAHhvGEULYdaYw8E1c07rohJKjr25P5tuwuB_chXqhdqSzfQIWNX9qYf3lNhmpzgXU9DAz3uBKNKheiHJAOQHogqMXcAV2wqVHtDmrBidMnba5Ydj6cwoG1rKj2W481McFkpUt9iXlNHO0FIcOpQG-e_bHlSZcHMSItCmKNbDYYYEfTnhmESkrJqS1SLa2r02aVRIxma-v6ftUF4QeLw8zljcMmWyna4HPQBYpok2aeYjfPJlfy3up0E9It-_Wf9WsvJhpjNvyrVLIgxIk-DWPehcyXI_bWg_lskuRy4SlhvV_NE5G2gAJGyqH2GyyWOT5GCpZ4JubcBoNrQtmuxsIp7waS" target="_blank"&gt;明显违反了宪法&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: 